Change and a smile from one of the last toll collectors in the Florida Keys

article_metadata.title: In the shadow of Key West, change ahead for a neighboring island | Miami Herald

og.description: In his Roostica Wood-Fire Pizzeria-branded pickup truck Thursday morning, Bobby Mongelli points out a Stock Island trailer park with 90 units -- and 400 people.
